name: Larry & Skeletor
description:
Based on a painting I did, this is former Boston Celtic Larry Bird having a casual conversation with his good friend, Skeletor, presumably about Magic Johnson and He-Man.

12" x 19" 4 color screen print on 100 lb French Poptone Berrylicious flavored paper. Signed and numbered edition of 35.

name: There's Always Pro Wrestlers At The Banana Stand
description:
Don't watch season 4 of Arrested Development without this piece of art commemorating what has been going on at the banana stand since we last saw the Bluths. Based on a painting I did of Hulk Hogan, Andre the Giant and Randy "Mr. Macho Manager" Savage hanging out at the O.C.'s favorite big yellow joint. 

12.5" x 19" 4 color screen print on French Banana Split Poptone 100 lb. cover stock. Signed and Numbered.
